reviewText: Disappointed that it was so short- could have included more footage

As a life long Dodger fan this is great!  Wish I had a copy of the four games in 1963!!!!!!!!!  four straight over the Yanks!!!!!!!!  but we lost one the same way later ... that's ok we beat the Yankees!!!!!!!!

NO COMPLAINTS. I'M A SATISFIED CUSTOMER.
THANK YOU,
ROGER
